definitions.definition: To have an unfortunate accident of some kind; to be killed, or come to harm .
To go astray ; to do something wrong.
To have a miscarriage ; to involuntarily abort a foetus .
To fail to achieve some purpose; to be unsuccessful, to go wrong (of a business, project etc.).
Of a letter etc.: to fail to reach its intended recipient .

main_definition: ( obsolete ) To have an unfortunate accident of some kind; to be killed, or come to harm . [14th–18th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( now rare ) To go astray ; to do something wrong. [from 14th c.]
To have a miscarriage ; to involuntarily abort a foetus . [from 16th c.]
To fail to achieve some purpose; to be unsuccessful, to go wrong (of a business, project etc.). [from 16th c.]
Of a letter etc.: to fail to reach its intended recipient . [from 16th c.]
